---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="MattPak — Customer Story — Formic"
  description="MattPak, an Illinois co-manufacturer juggling hundreds of SKUs, deployed three palletizing systems and started its automation journey without a six-figure capital outlay."
  ogTitle="MattPak — Formic Customer Story"
  ogDescription="3 palletizing systems · hundreds of SKUs · no big upfront cost"
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/stories/mattpak" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/stories">Customer Stories</a><span class="sep">/</span>MattPak
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Customer Story · MattPak</div>
    <h1 style="font-size:clamp(32px,3.8vw,56px)">Meeting Every Customer Need: How MattPak Scaled with Automation</h1>
    <p class="lede">MattPak, an Illinois co-manufacturer juggling hundreds of SKUs and dozens of customers' standards, deployed three palletizing systems — and started its automation journey without a six-figure capital outlay.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <img src="/stories/mattpak-hero.jpg" alt="MattPak co-manufacturing and palletizing" />
      <span class="dv-cap">MattPak · Illinois</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:64px 0 0">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 80px">
    <div class="db-tag">At a glance</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey);margin-top:14px">
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Location</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Illinois</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Industry</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Co-manufacturing</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Products</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">Spices, laundry & dishwasher pods</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Facility</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">55,000 → 100,000+ sq ft</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--white);padding:18px 20px"><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey);margin-bottom:6px">Formic systems</div><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:17px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.01em;color:var(--black)">3 palletizers</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — The Challenge</div>
      <h2>Everything for everyone, <em>all the time</em>.</h2>
      <p>As a co-manufacturer of spices, laundry pods, and dishwasher pods, MattPak manages hundreds of SKUs and the specific standards of dozens of customers. Manual palletizing — led by Co-Owner and Operations Manager Matt Kunach — was a high-injury-risk job. The team recognized automation as the future but wanted to start without a huge upfront investment.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Hundreds of SKUs and dozens of customer standards</li>
        <li>Manual palletizing — "high risk of injury"</li>
        <li>Wanted to try automation without a big upfront cost</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/mattpak-2.jpg" alt="MattPak automated palletizing system" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Three systems · minimal downtime</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0095.jpg" alt="Formic robotic palletizer" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Full Service · monthly</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — The Solution</div>
      <h2>Start somewhere, <em>then expand</em>.</h2>
      <p>Formic 3D-mapped the facility with augmented reality — a tool no competitor MattPak talked to could offer. Most palletizers the team reviewed ran over $150,000; Formic's Full Service monthly model removed that upfront wall. Three systems went in with minimal downtime, and case packing is next.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Augmented-reality 3D facility mapping</li>
        <li>Monthly model vs. $150,000+ per machine to buy</li>
        <li>Three systems deployed with minimal downtime</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:88px 80px">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;padding:0">
    <div class="pull-quote">
      <blockquote>"The big thing for us was wanting to try automation without making a huge upfront investment."</blockquote>
      <cite>Matt Kunach · Co-Owner & Operations Manager, MattPak</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">03 — The Outcome</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,72px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--white);margin:18px 0 56px">Built to <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">grow with demand.</em></h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">3</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Palletizing systems</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">$150k+</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Upfront cost avoided</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">2x</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Facility expansion</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Scale to meet <em>every need</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/stories" class="btn-ctawh">More Customer Stories</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
